description: Seller to CREDIT ONE YEAR of condo/parking fee!! Don't miss this stunning & stylish value proposition in prime South Boston location. One of the most sought after floor plans, this high floor 2 bed/2 bath also boasts an over-sized, private deck perfect for entertaining and relaxing; a city oasis.  Entry foyer with subway tiled guest bath and vanity storage.  Light & sun filled open plan living, dining and kitchen. Chef’s kitchen with island seating, Wolf, Subzero and Quartz counter tops facing floor to ceiling windows, private deck with additional Juliet balcony.  Full primary suite with walk in closet.  2nd bedroom is spacious and perfect for office and/or guests.  All this in a full service, modern amenity building w/ concierge, fitness center, fully loaded common roof deck and recreation room. Situated in coveted W. Broadway location within seconds to Seaport and the South End. In unit laundry, A/C & pet friendly.
